  "title": "Service Coordinator at Alexandra Rd, $2,800 – $3,300 (Office hours)",
  "description": "<p><strong>- 3-month contract (non-renewable)</strong></p><p><strong>- $2,800 – $3,300</strong></p><p><strong>- Mon to Fri, 8.45am – 5.30pm</strong></p><p><strong>- Alexandra Rd</strong><br /><strong></strong></p><p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Coordinate with service contractors and customers to<strong> schedule service appointments.</strong></li><li>Handle customer enquiries through multiple channels, including phone calls, emails, Live Chat, WhatsApp, and walk-in customers, ensuring timely and professional responses.</li><li>Compilation and preparation of Reports to the Management.</li><li>Any other duties as assigned by the Service Manager</li></ul><p></p><p><strong>Period:</strong></p><ul><li>3-month contract (non-renewable) </li></ul><p></p><p><strong>Location: </strong></p><ul><li>Alexandra Rd</li></ul><p></p><p><strong>Working Hours:</strong></p><ul><li>Mon to Fri, 8.45am – 5.30pm</li></ul><p></p><p><strong>Salary:</strong></p><ul><li>$2,800 – $3,300</li></ul><p></p><p><strong>Requirements:</strong><br /></p><ul><li>Diploma in Business Administration, or similar discipline</li><li>Minimum 3 years of relevant after-sales customer service experience.</li><li>Good analytical, organizational, and documentation skills.</li><li>Proficient in Microsoft Excel.</li><li>Able to work independently and communicate effectively with internal and external stakeholders.</li></ul><p></p><p>​Interested applicants, kindly email your detailed resume (MS Word format is preferred):</p><p><strong>wanyi@successhrc.com.sg</strong> (Reg No: <strong>R25128591</strong>)<br /></p><p>Please ensure that applications sent through email are no bigger than 1Mb.</p><p>We thank all applicants for your interest but regret to inform that only shortlisted candidates would be notified.<br /></p><p><strong>Success Resource Centre Pte Ltd</strong> (EA License Number: <strong>04C3201</strong>)</p><p>160 Robinson Road, #13-07/08/09 SBF Center, Singapore 068914</p><p>T: 6337 3183 | W: <a href=\"http://www.successhrc.com.sg/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">www.successhrc.com.sg</a></p>",
